  13 Jun 2015; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  Text-Format-0.580.0-r1.ebuild, Text-Format-0.590.0.ebuild:
  Module::Build is no longer part of core Perl and has been moved to dev-perl

  11 Jan 2015; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> Text-Format-0.590.0.ebuild:
  Stable for all

*Text-Format-0.580.0-r1 (23 Aug 2014)

  23 Aug 2014; Ian Stakenvicius (_AxS_) <axs@gentoo.org>
  +Text-Format-0.580.0-r1.ebuild, -Text-Format-0.580.0.ebuild:
  bumped current stable ebuild(s) EAPI to 5; committed directly to stable as no
  other changes present and revbump helps stable systems to keep from dieing on
  perl-5.18 upgrade

  31 May 2014; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> Text-Format-0.590.0.ebuild:
  Fix version in MODULE_VERSION

